text:
{
  "prompt": "A detailed technical diagram of a high-performance electric motorcycle platform. The layout is similar to an electric skateboard-style vehicle base with the following components: a large central rectangular battery pack (144V 200Ah) mounted low in the chassis, a central motor (8kW) connected to a 7-speed automatic gearbox with dog clutch mechanism, a chain or belt drive to the rear wheel. The front wheel (17-inch) is connected via telescopic suspension, and the rear wheel (15-inch) via dual shock absorbers. The frame is tubular steel with integrated cargo racks front and rear. Annotate the components clearly: battery pack, motor, 7-speed gearbox, suspension, wheels, and control electronics. White background, technical drawing style with slight 3D perspective.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A technical digital illustration of an electric motorcycle drivetrain with advanced suspension and powertrain layout. The image should be a side-view schematic showing: a 17-inch front wheel with telescopic fork suspension, a 144V 200Ah battery pack mounted low in a skateboard-style central tray, and a rear setup that includes an 8kW electric motor aligned with the direction of travel. The motor is connected to a 7-speed automatic transmission. Additionally, the seat is mounted independently with its own suspension system, separate from the dual rear shock absorbers on the swingarm. Highlight all three suspension points clearly: front fork, rear swingarm, and seat post. Use clear labeling and grayscale with technical shading.",
  "size": "1024x768"
}

{
  "prompt": "A technical side view drawing of an electric motorcycle without a traditional seat. The design features a skateboard-style frame with a centrally mounted 144V battery pack. The rear suspension is similar to that of a high-performance electric scooter (e.g., horizontal coilover or swingarm shock connected directly to the frame), independent of any seat structure. The seat is designed as a separate module mounted above the battery frame, not structurally tied to the suspension. The image uses clear black-and-white linework, highlighting front telescopic suspension, 8kW motor, 7-speed automatic transmission, and wide 15-inch rear tire.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
